            "title": "港股開市︱初段造好 恒指升216點報25280點 小米績後低開1.96%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">日韓等亞洲主要股市今早持續反彈，有助支持港股氣氛。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生指數開市報25280點，升216點或0.87%。恒生科技指數開報4878點，升47點或0.99%；國企指數以8559點開市，升60點或0.71%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股11.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股11.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">業績股仍是市場焦點，各家於昨天收市後派成績表的企業，今早股價互有升跌。小米(01810)今早開報32.05元，跌1.96%；海底撈(06862)開報15.35元，跌4%；中國電信(00728)開報4.87元，跌0.41%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">同在昨收市後公布業績的農夫山泉(09633)，今早則開報45元，升6.03%；萬洲國際(00288)開報9.88元，升5%；藥明生物(02269)開報34.24元，升1.06%。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：小米官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/bplib_20230703-123039__source-web_01810-1_source-web_-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：小米官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/bplib_20230703-123039__source-web_01810-1_source-web_-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：小米官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">理想汽車(02015)昨晚公布不超過10億美元的回購計畫，該股今早開報69.6元，升2.96%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">其他重磅股普遍造好，滙控(00005)開報124.4元，升0.65%；阿里巴巴(09988)開報125.2元，升1.62%；騰訊(00700)開報519元，升0.97%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15787858-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%88%9d%e6%ae%b5%e9%80%a0%e5%a5%bd-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e5%8d%87216%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b125280%e9%bb%9e-%e5%b0%8f%e7%b1%b3%e7%b8%be%e5%be%8c%e4%bd%8e%e9%96%8b1",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK.jpg.webp",
